data.description: Exciting news! The seller is offering to lower the interest rate for you! Welcome to this coveted home in Gladden Farms Community, renowned for its energy efficiency with cost-saving solar panels. Boasting 4 bedrooms, a loft, and 3 baths, this home offers abundant living space. Step inside to a serene ambiance with custom paint, neutral tile floors, plantation shutters, and ceiling fans throughout. The spacious kitchen features Corian counters, a large pantry, black appliances, patio access, and ample wood cabinets. Relax on plush carpets or charming laminate floors in the delightful loft area. Outside, revel in the grassy landscape, covered patio, and flagstone dining area in the backyard. Added comforts include surround sound and a soft water loop. Make this your home today!
